                                    <h2 class="h3 separator-left wow">Pre-settlement Funding</h2>
                                    <p>While a case is in progress, a cash advance payment may be needed for various expenses. <a href="https://www.oasisfinancial.com/how-it-works/">Pre-settlement funding</a> offers you <strong>a portion of your settlement upfront</strong>, allowing faster relief from overdue bills and financial worries. Also known as a lawsuit advance or settlement loan, this money is taken from what a plaintiff is estimated to receive once their case is finalized.</p>
